{"tid":1210831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【請幫手推】應該反其道而行去消耗對方，而唔係留係度被對方消耗！","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:03:03.000Z","uid":152123,"like":204,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"99bf15eedcb7a5c812de544da4407cec64d79124","tid":1210831,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"死守佔領=消耗自己體力，物資有限，精神狀態愈來愈差，好快會有無力感，人一少就被人總攻清場<br />\n<br />\n效法黃背心無限loop式示威、癱瘓式罷工、打遊擊<br />\n=<br />\n對方出動軍事成本一定被你高，所有子彈裝甲警車水炮等等、同埋人力成本都係遠高過示威者，而佢哋每日full gear裝備上陣其實好重，精神壓力會愈來愈大，體力消耗大過示威者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吸取雨傘教訓 反其道消耗對方<br />\n唔好重蹈覆轍留係度 慘被消耗</span></span>"},{"pid":"29cc6515be95301973da4145c9eacb555828d1c2","tid":1210831,"uid":126054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"要選擇係某段時間合法去做,由我地主導<br />\n唔想被影響/或認同我地既自然唔會影響<br />\n想挑戰我地,或唔關心既要接受後果"},{"pid":"53fb2df059ee176b2bac2fdaad780affc9b9a0d1","tid":1210831,"uid":53026,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"而且大匪狗尚未宣佈何時開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc419d52b72e95fa698a81c5b629af747c8c319","tid":1210831,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"今晚要守 ok<br />\nbe water<br />\n眼見直播啲人企喺到成碌木噉真係<br />\n鄧佢地慘，係咪太精神bun緊？"},{"pid":"237a3c2cde61e74047c8c8ddea77b5d752e9c84c","tid":1210831,"uid":152123,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"上次雨傘就係輸在被對方消耗精神 物資 體力<br />\n大家要切記<br />\n反其道去撚死班仆街<br />\n三日唔埋兩日就爆佢一鑊勁<br />\n社會上 一定要瘋狂批判你身邊嘅警察<br />\n朋友 親戚 一律批判<br />\n參考紅衛兵做法 反其道批鬥到佢哋意志力薄弱為止"},{"pid":"9988b83be1afce9c018023649429cda627b53a76","tid":1210831,"uid":108337,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"你睇下旺角幾多人仲嘻嘻哈哈食飯玩"},{"pid":"13bb591601d1efcd996748626270dcb15db640a3","tid":1210831,"uid":61443,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c874ee1dfaba84199b678c9965be95701577d35","tid":1210831,"uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"人點打你 你就從中學習點樣反攻<br />\n唔好重複同樣嘅錯誤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/16/Repetitive_error.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070902105305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F16%2FRepetitive_error.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070902105305&h=b7a3ba40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8830f4755004acf45048370a8db9138de305752","tid":1210831,"uid":47252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d5908eeb261e8d9443ba85b1d510f8849633d06a","tid":1210831,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"人地輪更全副武裝有休息<br />\n唔好再講啲咁弱智嘅嘢<br />\n你唔會消耗到"},{"pid":"2717f9c5e237acef5734c0dd921981bb0e1587c1","tid":1210831,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有關雨傘輸在被消耗嘅學者研究</span></span><br />\n有興趣請自己睇，唔翻譯全文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYuen, S. and Cheng, E. (2017). Neither Repression Nor Concession? A Regime&rsquo;s Attrition against Mass Protests. Political Studies, 65(3), pp.611-630.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/pdf/10.1177/0032321716674024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1177%2F0032321716674024&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=088252b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://journal